An Inter City Express (ICE) train is standing on track 7 of Frankfurt main station after an 8-year-old boy was run over and killed on Monday. German police said a man pushed the boy and his mother onto the tracks. The mother escaped, but the boy died. Four tracks were closed. Photo: IC   
